		<h2 class="editor-block--title" id="heading-ykwn7x5zdp">Key points</h2>
		</div>
		<div class="dfe-section__content">
		<ul class="nested-list">
<li class="level-1">CDC is responding to an outbreak of Ebola disease in remote areas of the Democratic Republic of the Congo (DRC) and Uganda.</li>
<li class="level-1">To date, no cases of Ebola disease have been confirmed in the United States because of this outbreak.</li>
<li class="level-1">The overall risk to the American public and travelers remains low.</li>
</ul>
